{"tid":1509087,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"G7峯會聲明支持港自治 重申《中英聯合聲明》存在而且重要","createTime":"2019-08-26T17:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T07:09:21.000Z","uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f5fd331bf6328dc7ab79401d36a0d946b6afc686","tid":1509087,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"在法國舉行的七大工業國集團（G7）峯會周一結束，會後發表的簡短聯合聲明提到香港，表示支持香港自治，並呼籲各方冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提到，「G7重申1984年《中英聯合聲明》的存在與重要性，呼籲避免暴力」。<br />\n<br />\n與會的英國首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）亦表示，繼續致力於維護香港一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n由「反送中」引發的示威浪潮，持續近三個月仍未平息，周日警方首次開真槍，並動用水炮，有外媒形容警民衝突暴力升級。<br />\n<br />\n除了香港，G7聲明亦提到貿易、伊朗、利比亞和烏克蘭問題，指七大工業國致力維持開放公平的國際貿易體系以及全球經濟穩定。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提到，希望世界貿易組織有相當的改變，使之更有效率於保護知識產權，更迅速解決糾紛，消除不公平貿易行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190827/59977051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F59977051&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrvlfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=175081a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F59977051&h=2cd7acc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190827/59977051</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbcdb98cd6d3cb32aff1cb02f796502d390e7862","tid":1509087,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrvlfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=7d270e9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/st